summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing the execution of an agreement with the State of Washington for the improvement of Denny Way from Westlake Avenue to Western Avenue, excluding the intersection at Aurora Avenue and Denny Way, by widening streets, constructing traffic channelization, construction of signal improvements, signal interconnects, widening, channelization, illumination, signing, landscaping and incidental work under the Federal Aid "M" Program - Federal Aid Project No. M-3544(1).
